{"type": "article", "id": 25119, "title": "你能从这个姑娘的“疯帽子”里找到多少电影的痕迹？", "description": "感觉非常适合德普来一顶。", "date": "2016-04-08T07:15:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1531, "name": "帽子"}, {"id": 25949, "name": "制帽匠"}, {"id": 25950, "name": "Teri Aldersey"}], "category": 17, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 114, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607180408N30XlOsMykhDJTz7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">今年 40 岁的 Teri Aldersey 来自英国北林肯郡（North Lincolnshire），因为受到 2010 年的电影《爱丽丝梦游仙境》中约翰尼·德普饰演的疯帽子一角的启发，她设计了一系列新奇好看的帽子。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071804022zfyvnSIQku6gJ58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Aldersey 自封为现实版的“疯帽子”。谈到将于这周末在安特里（Aintree）举行的赛马大会时，她承认这些帽子比其它可能出现的花式礼帽要吸睛得多。不少帽子都带着蒸汽朋克风格，大多以流行文化为主题，除了《爱丽丝漫游仙境》之外，你可以从中发现《加勒比海盗》、《哈利·波特》还有《圣诞夜惊魂》的影子。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180403iDWpTxocfXHKatuP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180403tycf3zQ7DFUp2Jem.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180404Y7LnfyhrzpMqO4TV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180404f6SAetKLRTvokQ9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180405aJvsPnziwpAhBEUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180406p0RaPCdHvYhUfwBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180406QHKAUtqmLpVh9viw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071804070J2tNqh5QMluFIKE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你对她的设计感兴趣，还可以去她的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/OohLaLaBoudoir\">网店</a>看看。</p>\n<p class=\"\">文中图片来自 Fortitude Press/Barcroft Media</p>\n\n\n"}